<para>X (<xref linkend="xfree86"/> or <xref linkend="xorg"/>) and 
<xref linkend="esound"/> or <acronym>OSS</acronym> or 
<xref linkend="alsa"/> or <xref linkend="arts"/></para>
</sect4>

